name: The Secrets She Keeps
overview: In an affluent Sydney suburb, two women have a chance encounter in a supermarket. They are the same age, both heavily pregnant and due at the same time. Meghan is a glamorous influencer on the rise, with an ambitious television sports reporter husband Jack, while Agatha works in the supermarket as a shelf stacker. Although they live near each other, the two women’s lives could not be more different…Both women have secrets. And both will risk everything to conceal the truth. But their worlds are about to collide in one shocking act that cannot be undone.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Two years after Agatha Fyfle kidnapped her baby, explosive secrets will spin Meghan Shaughnessy onto a catastrophic and ultimately fatal course, while Agatha's new obsession sees them collide in a way that no one will anticipate.

tagline: The life she wanted wasn't hers.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Heavily pregnant supermarket shelf-stacker Agatha is obsessed with Meghan Shaughnessy's seemingly perfect life. But is there more to her covetous gaze than simply admiration?

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Meghan's explosive secret comes to light. With Meghan's due date brought forward, Agatha must step up her plans.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: A scarring trauma in Agatha's past is revealed. Meghan heads to hospital to have her baby, unaware that she might be in danger.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Agatha has created her perfect family with her baby and Hayden. But an old flame of Agatha's threatens to thwart her plans.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: At a vigil for Baby Ben, Meghan and Agatha come face-to-face. Agatha panics over Baby Rory's deteriorating health.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Agatha is on the run with Baby Rory. Will Meghan get her baby boy back?

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Two years have passed since her child was kidnapped, and someone is dead as Meghan Shaughnessy is being held by police for murder.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Agatha is determined to keep her pregnancy safe; Meghan comes face to face with Grace's suspicions over Ben's paternity.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Agatha's quest for help reveals a twist; Meghan faces the loss of her marriage when the truth of Ben's paternity is revealed.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: As Meghan's life spins out of control, the devastating truth of who she has killed is finally revealed – and, when Agatha is hospitalized after a severe beating in jail, their paths will again collide.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: In prison with Agatha, the grief-stricken Meghan navigates a nightmare, while Agatha's dream of motherhood seems destined to be stripped away by forces outside her control.

episodes.overview: In a thrilling finale to the series, Agatha and Meghan face their hardest trials yet – but with an explosive ending that neither will see coming.
